{"tid":1432584,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際大行動！】9月17日聯合國大會開幕","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T10:14:00.000Z","uid":125508,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e75f5d85238213822697d1c98b38cc03e5969d3c","tid":1432584,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:19:09.000Z","msg":"G20峰會，托連登各路英雄所賜，發動全球連環眾籌登報，及後有人組團赴日請願陳情反送中議題，令香港問題得到國際社會注意，運動得到國際聲援和反響。<br />\n但還有比G20更刺激，更廣泛，更高難度的一關，就是9月中的聯合國大會。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9月17日聯合國大會將在紐約開幕</span></strong>，24日進入大會辯論環節。<br />\n聯合國大會網站：<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/ga/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fga%2F&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7yWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=ecfb2b3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.un.org/en/ga/</a><br />\n聯合國大會一年召開一次，重點節目是聯合國審議法案，以及<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各國元首到場演說（包括維尼熊、侵侵）</span></strong></span>。<br />\n為了爭取更多國際支持，讓恐怖主義政府跪地求饒，盡情掃落中共的面子，實現普選，實現訴求。<br />\n各路英雄，是時候發動<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>萬國聯軍</strong></span>了！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，再創輝煌</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"464b100546473a76bc23bf3fc3ae59eecce8165f","tid":1432584,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"c94b0417bc48ca491b7569384860f4ca0c9f9197","tid":1432584,"uid":141508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87942696288f1c2ba3a1529762aec21c9916a383","tid":1432584,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e884430aa444d65ec9658be089a6d85a4a7b4e32","tid":1432584,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:24:09.000Z","msg":"萬國聯軍擊殺"},{"pid":"42d21